;-*-*                         Insertion Sort                          *-*-
;-*-*                                                                 *-*-
;-*-*                       Wolfgang De Meuter                        *-*-
;-*-*                 2008 Programming Technology Lab                 *-*-
;-*-*                   Vrije Universiteit Brussel                    *-*-
;-*-*                                                                 *-*-
